      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Tamás Kuzmics</b>\n</p><p><b>Tamás Kuzmics</b>, <br />\na Hungarian web developer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and computer chess programmer. He is author of the <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/TomitankChess\" title=\"TomitankChess\">tomitankChess</a>, written in <a href=\"/JavaScript\" title=\"JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>, also available as <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mobile_app\">mobile app</a> <b>Chess</b> or <b>Sakk</b> under <a href=\"/Android\" title=\"Android\">Android</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=IOS&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"IOS (page does not exist)\">iOS</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2017_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tam%C3%A1s_Kuzmics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017_...\">2017 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tam%C3%A1s_Kuzmics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2017 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63948\">Update Best Score and Best Move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 10, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Best_Move\" title=\"Best Move\">Best Move</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=64343\">Tuning Futility Margin</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 19, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=64428\">Mate Score</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 27, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Checkmate#MateScore\" title=\"Checkmate\">Mate Score</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=64706\">IID (skipped when in check and Score greater than alpha)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=64803\">Delta pruning Mate error</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 04, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Delta_Pruning\" title=\"Delta Pruning\">Delta Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=64827\">Evasion (capture) moves ordering by See</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 06, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64853\">Fifty move counter and Null move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 09, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Fifty-move_Rule\" title=\"Fifty-move Rule\">Fifty-move Rule</a>, <a href=\"/Halfmove_Clock\" title=\"Halfmove Clock\">Halfmove Clock</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65198\">JavaScript Pawn Bitboard (with 32 bit integers)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 17, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/JavaScript\" title=\"JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>, <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65200\">tomitankChess - New JavaScript engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 17, 2017 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=65344\">Strongest JavaScript Chess Engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 30, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=65448\">Magic BitBoards Magic numbers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 14, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=65479\">check evasions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 18, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Check\" title=\"Check\">Check</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65899\">tomitankChess v.1.5</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 03, 2017</li></ul>\n<p><b>2018</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66914\">Small improvement</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 24, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67279\">Where is bug?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 29, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67693\">Small improve for Blockers and Beyond Bitboard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 10, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Blockers_and_Beyond\" title=\"Blockers and Beyond\">Blockers and Beyond</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67893\">Texel Tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 03, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67954\">tomitankChess 2.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 11, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69207&amp;start=1\">Re: Gradient Descent Introduction</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 09, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2019</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67524&amp;start=3\">Re: Poor man's neurones</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 28, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70185\">Stockfish Skill-Level</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 12, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tam%C3%A1s_Kuzmics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72894\">tomitankChess 4.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73377\">Mobile application</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 15, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75188\">tomitankChess 4.2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 23, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75925\">Pawn King Neural Network</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tamás Kuzmics</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 26, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tam%C3%A1s_Kuzmics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/tomitank\">tomitank (Kuzmics Tamás) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tam%C3%A1s-kuzmics-a225931b6/\">Tamás Kuzmics | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Kuzmics+Tam%C3%A1s+/tomitank/&amp;hl=en\">Android Apps by Kuzmics Tamás /tomitank/ on Google Play</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/developer/tamas-kuzmics/id1150654414\">Tamas Kuzmics Apps on the App Store</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\